<div class="body typo-l">
  <p><strong>Open source</strong> authors and contributors need much <strong>more love</strong> from the community.</p>
  <p>Those who initiate and share their projects, as well as those who participate and collaborate to constantly improve them, merit a <strong>big thank-you</strong>.</p>
  <p>The intent behind <strong><em>Yo, This is Cool</em></strong> is having a space where you can thank the amazing people behind your favorite open source projects on GitHub.</p>

  <hr/>

  <h3>Credits</h3>
  <p>This site is conceived and created with love by <a href="http://github.com/alpacaaa" target="_blank" title="Marco Sampellegrini on GitHub">Marco Sampellegrini</a> and <a href="http://www.andreaburan.com" target="_blank" title="Andrea Buran’s Sitefolio">Andrea Buran</a>.</p>
  <p>It is designed and developed in the mighty <a href="http://emberjs.com/" target="_blank">Ember.js</a> + <a href="http://loopback.io/" target="_blank">Loopback</a> and vigorous <a href="http://sass-lang.com/" target="_blank">SCSS</a> + <a href="http://compass-style.org/" target="_blank">Compass</a> tandems, with the help of <a href="http://html5boilerplate.com/" target="_blank">HTML5 Boilerplate</a> and <a href="http://packery.metafizzy.co/" target="_blank">Packery</a>.</p>
  <p>The font is <a href="http://www.google.com/fonts/specimen/Roboto" target="_blank">Roboto</a> by Google while the emoji are <a href="http://twitter.github.io/twemoji/" target="_blank">Twit Emoji</a> by Twitter.</p>

  <h3>Help and Spread the Word</h3>
  <p>If you would like to help and spread the word about the project, here is a <a href="https://yothisis.cool/yothisiscool.png" title="Pic of Meri the Mandragora">link to a pic</a> of <em>Yo, This is Cool</em>’s beautiful mascot <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mandragora_officinarum" target="_blank" title="Mandragora on Wikipedia">Meri the Mandragora</a> you can share<sup id="fnref:share"><a href="#fn:share">2</a></sup> with others.</p>

  <h3>Contribute and Touch Base</h3>
  <p>If in addition you would like to contribute to the project<sup id="fnref:contribute"><a href="#fn:contribute">3</a></sup> and touch base with us, feel free to wander around <a href="https://github.com/alpacaaa/dude" target="_blank" title="Yo, This is Cool GitHub repository"><em>Yo, This is Cool</em> GitHub repository</a> and drop us a line at <a href="mailto:hey@yothisis.cool" target="_blank">hey@yothisis.cool</a>.</p>

